"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?30/49/31509?source=related_link\">",
"      Occipital neuralgia",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/10/11431?source=related_link\">",
"      Overview of craniofacial pain",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?17/29/17882?source=related_link\">",
"      Stevens-Johnson syndrome and toxic epidermal necrolysis: Clinical manifestations; pathogenesis; and diagnosis",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
